            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1.1">Describe the bug</st>
            <st ob="x" eb="" sr="" id="1.2">In Accuracy view, if you type a negative sign into the latitude, longitude, or altitude text boxes, nothing happens (no negative signs are added).</st>
